Uses of Package
org.alljoyn.ns.commons

  • Packages that use org.alljoyn.ns.commons 
    Package Description
    org.alljoyn.ns
    The package includes API classes of the Notification service which are used to send and receive notification messages
    org.alljoyn.ns.commons
    The package includes generic classes that are used by other packages of the Notification service
    org.alljoyn.ns.nativeplatform
    The package includes classes with the platform dependent logic.
  • Classes in org.alljoyn.ns.commons used by org.alljoyn.ns 
    Class and Description
    GenericLogger
    Implement this interface to provide logging functionality for the Notification service
  • Classes in org.alljoyn.ns.commons used by org.alljoyn.ns.commons 
    Class and Description
    GenericLogger
    Implement this interface to provide logging functionality for the Notification service
    NativePlatform
    Implement this interface to provide platform dependent functionality for the Notification service
    NativePlatformFactoryException
    The exception is thrown if there was a failure in loading and instantiating the class implementing platform dependent logic
  • Classes in org.alljoyn.ns.commons used by org.alljoyn.ns.nativeplatform 
    Class and Description

    Implement this interface to provide logging functionality for the Notification service
